\c 37
\s Areka, netafura, nemwenje, nearitari yezvinonhuhwira
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bhezareri akaita areka yamatanda omuakasia; kureba kwayo kwaiva makubhiti maviri nehafu, noupamhi hwayo kubhiti rimwe nehafu, nokukwirira kwayo kubhiti rimwe nehafu,
\v 2 akaifukidza nendarama yakaisvonaka nechomukati nechokunze, akaita pamusoro payo hata yendarama yakaipoteredza.
\v 3 Akaiumbira zvindori zvina zvendarama, akazviisa pamakumbo ayo mana; zvindori zviviri zvaiva parutivi rumwe, nezvindori zviviri panorumwe rutivizve.
\v 4 Akaveza matanda omuakasia, akaafukidza nendarama,
\v 5 akapinza matanda iwayo muzvindori zvaiva panhivi dzeareka, kuti areka itakurwe nawo.
\p
\v 6 Akaitawo chifunhiro chokuyananisa nendarama yakaisvonaka; kureba kwacho kwaiva makubhiti maviri nehafu, noupamhi hwacho kubhiti rimwe nehafu;
\v 7 akaita makerubhi maviri endarama, akaaita nendarama yakapambadzirwa pamiromo miviri yechifunhiro chokuyananisa,
\v 8 kerubhi rimwe pamuromo mumwe, nerimwe kerubhi panomumwe muromo; akaita makerubhi pamiromo yacho miviri, zvikava chinhu chimwe chete nechifunhiro chokuyananisa.
\v 9 Makerubhi akange akatambanudzira mapapiro awo kumusoro, akafukidza chifunhiro chokuyananisa namapapiro awo, zviso zvawo zvakatarisana; zviso zvamakerubhi zvakange zvakatarira chifunhiro chokuyananisa.
\p
\v 10 Akaitawo tafura yamatanda omuakasia; kureba kwayo kwaiva makubhiti maviri, noupamhi hwayo kubhiti rimwe, nokukwirira kwayo kubhiti rimwe nehafu.
\v 11 Akaifukidza nendarama yakaisvonaka, akaiitirawo hata yendarama yakange ichiipoteredza;
\v 12 akaiitirawo ukomba hwakange huchiipoteredza, upamhi hwahwo sechanza; akaiitirawo hata yendarama yaipoteredza ukomba hwayo.
\v 13 Akaiitira zvindori zvina zvendarama, akaisa zvindori pamakona mana aiva pamakumbo ayo mana.
\v 14 Zvindori zvaiva pedo noukomba, paiva pokutakura tafura napo namatanda.
\v 15 Akaita matanda omuakasia, akaafukidza nendarama, kuti tafura itakurwe nawo.
\v 16 Akaitawo midziyo yaigara pamusoro petafura, ndiro dzayo, nembiya dzayo, nemikombe yayo, nezvirongo zvayo zvokudira nazvo, zvese zvendarama yakaisvonaka.
\p
\v 17 Akaitawo chigadziko chemwenje chendarama yakaisvonaka; akaita chigadziko nendarama yakapambadzirwa, chigadziko chacho, nehunde yacho, notumbiya twacho, namafundo acho, namaruva acho; zvese zvikava chinhu chimwe chete nacho;
\v 18 kumativi acho kukabuda matavi matanhatu, matavi matatu echigadziko kuno rumwe rutivi rwacho, namatavi matatu echigadziko kuno rumwe rutivi rwacho.
\v 19 Tumbiya tutatu twakaumbwa samaruva omuamanda padavi rimwe, nefundo neruva, notumbiya tutatuzve twakaumbwa samaruva omuamanda pane rimwe davi, nefundo neruva; saizvozvo matavi matanhatu akabuda pachigadziko.
\v 20 Uye pachigadziko pakange panotumbiya tuna twakange twakaumbwa samaruva omuamanda, namafundo atwo, namaruva atwo;
\v 21 nefundo panyasi pamatavi maviri akange akaumbwa pamwechete nacho; nefundozve panyasi pamatavi maviri akaumbwa pamwechete nacho, akafanana namatavi matanhatu akabuda pachigadziko.
\v 22 Mafundo azvo namatavi akange akaumbwa pamwechete nazvo, zvese zvikava chinhu chimwe chakange chakumbwa nendarama yakaisvonaka, yakapambadzirwa.
\v 23 Akaita mwenje yacho minomwe, nembato dzacho, nendiro dzacho, zvese nendarama yakaisvonaka.
\v 24 Akachiumba netarenda rendarama yakaisvonaka, pamwechete nemidziyo yayo yese.
\p
\v 25 Akaitawo aritari yezvinonhuhwira nomuakasia; kureba kwayo kwakange kuri kubhiti rimwe, noupamhi hwayo kubhiti rimwezve; nhivi dzese ina dzakange dzakaenzana; kukwirira kwayo kwaiva makubhiti maviri, nenyanga dzayo dzakange dziri chinhu chimwe chete nayo.
\v 26 Akaifukidza nendarama yakaisvonaka, kumusoro kwayo, nenhivi dzayo dzese, nenyanga dzayo; akaiitirawo hata yendarama yakange yakaipoteredza.
\v 27 Akaiitirawo zvindori zviviri zvendarama pasi pehata yayo, pakona dzayo mbiri panhivi dzayo mbiri, pakava pokuitakura napo namatanda.
\v 28 Akaitawo matanda omuakasia, akaafukidza nendarama.
\p
\v 29 Akaitawo mafuta matsvene okuzodza nawo, nezvinonhuhwira zvakaisvonaka zvemiti inonaka, zvikava zvakavhenganiswa nouchenjeri hwomuvhenganisi wezvinonhuhwira.
